**Idea:** 
* Greedy and 2 pointers
* Sort both the arrays and maintain pointers at each array
* Move cookie pointer until greed at current pointer is greater than or equal to cookie-size at current pointer. 
* Move greed pointer when condition is satisfied and increment count
